11:22.180 --> 11:25.740
 energy can change the way that other things behave.

11:25.740 --> 11:29.180
 It can cause reactions in cells of your body.

11:29.180 --> 11:32.000
 It can cause reactions in fruit, for instance, right?

11:32.000 --> 11:34.320
 You see a piece of fruit and it's not ripe,

