45:21.520 --> 45:25.380
 The first mechanism we could easily map to melatonin

45:25.380 --> 45:28.000
 and the fact that melatonin is suppressive

45:28.000 --> 45:31.440
 to various aspects of the so-called gonadal axis,

45:31.440 --> 45:34.020
