 If they received enough exposure of that light

49:39.180 --> 49:44.100
 to their skin, there were increases in testosterone

49:44.100 --> 49:46.980
 that were observed within a very brief period of time,

49:46.980 --> 49:50.060
 also increases in the hormone estrogen.

