 for instance, aggressiveness or in passionate feelings

50:34.800 --> 50:38.660
 and how their perception of other people changed

50:38.660 --> 50:42.340
 when they were getting a lot of UVB light exposure

50:42.340 --> 50:43.200
 to the skin.

